  <li><a href="https://gitter.im/guzzle/guzzle">Gitter</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="installing-guzzle">Installing Guzzle</h2>

<p>The recommended way to install Guzzle is through
<a href="https://getcomposer.org/">Composer</a>.</p>

<p><code>bash
composer require guzzlehttp/guzzle
</code></p>

